    <title>Arctic contributor: Glen Jeffries</title>
    <description>Glen Jeffries is a lawyer and writer based in Tromsø, in north Norway. Originally from the United Kingdom, he has studied and worked in Oxford, London and New York. He moved to Norway in 2016 to focus on marine and environmental law in the polar regions (and to learn to traverse snow gracefully). He likes to write about whales, the wilds and wrestling.
</description>
